    "body" : "<p>As already mentioned earlier. You could autowire <strong>Environment</strong>:</p>\n<pre><code>@Autowired\nprivate Environment environment;\n</code></pre>\n<p>only you could do check for the needed environment much easier:</p>\n<pre><code>if (environment.acceptsProfiles(Profiles.of(&quot;test&quot;))) {\n    doStuffForTestEnv();\n} else {\n    doStuffForOtherProfiles();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
