    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>with spring 5.3.28, things could be simpler:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>autowire <code>Environment</code>;</li>\n<li>use <code>boolean matchesProfiles(String... profileExpressions)</code>;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>for example:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>@Autowired\nprivate Environment environment;\n\n...\n\nif (env.matchesProfiles(&quot;online&quot;)) {\n  ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
