    "answer_id" : 77262475,
    "question_id" : 9267799,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h3>use service in spring boot</h3>\n<pre><code>@Service\nclass ProfileService(\n    val environment: Environment\n) {\n    fun get(): Profile? {\n        return Profile[environment.activeProfiles.firstOrNull()]\n    }\n\n    fun isTest(): Boolean {\n        return get() != Profile.PRD\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
